data.description: Welcome Home! Cozy country living awaits you in this charming 3 bed, 2 bath home on 5 acres! With 1800 sq ft of space, you'll have plenty of room to relax and enjoy the peaceful surroundings. Don't miss out on this perfect slice of country paradise! Move in Ready!!  Wood Burning Fireplace in Living Room.  The Refrigerator, Stove, Dishwasher, Microwave, Washer, and Dryer stay with home. Brand new LVP Flooring throughout. HVAC unit is New. Fresh Paint. New Lighting and Ceiling Fans.  Great Location, just a few minutes to the Interstate, the lake and Local Shopping
